---
// Эпическая прогрессия персонажей
---

<div class="rules-section">
  <h3>Эпическая прогрессия персонажа</h3>

  <div class="rule-block">
    <p>После достижения 20 уровня (228 ОП):</p>
    <p><strong>За каждые следующие 20 ОП персонаж получает одно из:</strong></p>
    <ul>
      <li>Эпический дар</li>
      <li>Черту</li>
      <li>+2 к характеристике (максимум 30)</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="note"><strong>Примечание:</strong> Если характеристика достигла 30, её больше нельзя повышать.</p>
  </div>

  <h3>Таблица эпических даров (d26)</h3>

  <table class="boons-table">
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>1</td>
        <td>Boon of Combat Prowess</td>
        <td>13</td>
        <td>Boon of Peerless Aim</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>2</td>
        <td>Boon of Dimensional Travel</td>
        <td>14</td>
        <td>Boon of Perfect Health</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>3</td>
        <td>Boon of Fate</td>
        <td>15</td>
        <td>Boon of Planar Travel</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>4</td>
        <td>Boon of the Fire Soul</td>
        <td>16</td>
        <td>Boon of Quick Casting</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>5</td>
        <td>Boon of Fortitude</td>
        <td>17</td>
        <td>Boon of Recovery</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>6</td>
        <td>Boon of High Magic</td>
        <td>18</td>
        <td>Boon of Resilience</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>7</td>
        <td>Boon of Immortality</td>
        <td>19</td>
        <td>Boon of Skill Proficiency</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>8</td>
        <td>Boon of Invincibility</td>
        <td>20</td>
        <td>Boon of Speed</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>9</td>
        <td>Boon of Irresistible Offense</td>
        <td>21</td>
        <td>Boon of Spell Mastery</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>10</td>
        <td>Boon of Luck</td>
        <td>22</td>
        <td>Boon of Spell Recall</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>11</td>
        <td>Boon of Magic Resistance</td>
        <td>23</td>
        <td>Boon of the Stormborn</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>12</td>
        <td>Boon of the Night Spirit</td>
        <td>24</td>
        <td>Boon of Truesight</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td colspan="2"></td>
        <td>25</td>
        <td>Boon of Undetectability</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td colspan="2"></td>
        <td>26</td>
        <td>Boon of the Unfettered</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</div>

<style>
  .rules-section {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
    box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
  }

  h3 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--heading-color);
  }

  h3:first-child {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .rule-block {
    background: var(--bg-primary);
    padding: 1rem;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent-color);
    margin: 1rem 0;
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
  }

  p {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  ul {
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .note {
    background: var(--bg-primary);
    padding: 0.75rem;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--warning-color);
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  td {
    padding: 0.75rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
  }

  tr:nth-child(even) {
    background: var(--bg-primary);
  }

  tr:hover {
    background: var(--accent-color);
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  td:first-child,
  td:nth-child(3) {
    width: 40px;
    text-align: center;
    font-weight: 600;
    background: var(--accent-color);
    color: white;
  }

  tr:nth-child(even) td:first-child,
  tr:nth-child(even) td:nth-child(3) {
    background: var(--accent-color);
    color: white;
  }
</style>
